                           protected function §8U§(event:SecurityErrorEvent) : void
                           {

                                 flag METADATA

                                                                              public function §@A§() : void
                                                                              {

                                                                                    flag METADATA

                                                                                       item "pos" "24038"
                                                                                    end ; metadata
                                                                                    dispid 0
                                                                                    method
                                                                                       name "com.angrybirds.avatarcreatorpopup:AvatarCreatorPopup/updateMenuToMatchEquippedItems"
                                                                                       returns QName(PackageNamespace(""),"void")
                                                                                       
                                                                                       body
                                                                                          maxstack 5
                                                                                          localcount 7
